content: नालिः --ली {%<ab>f.</ab>%} [नल्-णिच् इन् वा ङीप्] {@--1@} Any tubular vessel of the body. {@--2@} A hollow stalk, especially that of the lotus. {@--3@} A period of 24 minutes (घटिका). {@--4@} An instrument for boring an elephant's ear. {@--5@} A canal, drain. {@--6@} A lotusflower. {@--7@} A piece of metal on which the hours are struck (घटी).
